<title>缅甸公布最新伤亡情况</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E4%BC%A4%E4%BA%A1%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5</link>
